1
00:01:27,360 --> 00:01:34,320
=Hold a Court Now=

2
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:38,460
=Episode 8=

3
00:01:59,767 --> 00:02:03,239
♪All the little things
between you and me♪

4
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:06,240
♪Woven into our lives♪

5
00:02:06,770 --> 00:02:08,749
♪The building blocks of life♪

6
00:02:08,750 --> 00:02:10,449
♪Shape the sky above us♪

7
00:02:10,450 --> 00:02:12,929
♪Are you doing alright?♪

8
00:02:12,930 --> 00:02:15,930
♪What are you struggling for?♪

9
00:02:16,490 --> 00:02:20,630
♪Some questions weigh like mountains♪

10
00:02:20,690 --> 00:02:25,860
♪How do we piece life back together?♪

11
00:02:26,100 --> 00:02:30,289
♪So hate can fade
and love feels new again♪

12
00:02:30,290 --> 00:02:33,359
♪Reclaim the barren parts of life♪

13
00:02:33,360 --> 00:02:40,050
♪Walking this road together,
still hoping♪

14
00:02:40,520 --> 00:02:44,399
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

15
00:02:44,400 --> 00:02:46,509
According to the "Civil Code
of the People's Republic of China",

16
00:02:46,510 --> 00:02:48,159
(Family Court)
Article 1130...

17
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:48,679
Speak nicely!

18
00:02:48,680 --> 00:02:51,069
- Heirs who have made contributions
- Stop making noise!

19
00:02:51,070 --> 00:02:52,159
- in supporting the deceased,
- Don't make noise!

20
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,839
or lived with and cared for the deceased

21
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,999
- may receive a larger share.
- Pull him away!

22
00:02:56,000 --> 00:02:57,159
Heirs who are capable

23
00:02:57,160 --> 00:02:58,839
of supporting the deceased

24
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,279
yet failed
to fulfill their duty of support

25
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:03,560
may receive a smaller share
of the inheritance or none at all.

26
00:03:06,240 --> 00:03:09,029
According to the "Civil Code
of the People's Republic of China",

27
00:03:09,030 --> 00:03:11,356
Article 1067,

28
00:03:11,357 --> 00:03:14,189
children who do not fulfill
their duty of support,

29
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:15,439
lack the ability to work,

30
00:03:15,440 --> 00:03:16,879
or in financial difficulty,

31
00:03:16,880 --> 00:03:20,189
parents have the right to request
their children for maintenance.

32
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,789
I was wrong!

33
00:03:21,790 --> 00:03:24,510
Please forgive me
just this once, all right?

34
00:03:26,940 --> 00:03:30,679
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

35
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:32,439
Every time you judge,

36
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,839
you must consider seriously

37
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,749
the client's core demand.

38
00:03:35,750 --> 00:03:37,279
But you must respect
the client's opinion.

39
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,959
Who are you
to look down on me and educate me?

40
00:03:38,960 --> 00:03:39,509
He is just

41
00:03:39,510 --> 00:03:40,999
an inhumane judging machine.

42
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:43,189
You have so many cases.
Can't you mediate a single one?

43
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,189
You are a judge.

44
00:03:44,190 --> 00:03:45,749
You need to fulfill
the organized request.

45
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:47,159
Just become a terminator

46
00:03:47,160 --> 00:03:49,040
instead of being in the family court.

47
00:03:50,000 --> 00:03:57,839
♪And within every heart♪

48
00:03:57,840 --> 00:03:59,720
(Good morning)

49
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:17,239
(Since I have no work,)

50
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,680
(I should keep sleeping.)

51
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,320
Come in.

52
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,950
Master, you should eat something first.

53
00:04:42,600 --> 00:04:45,189
This is the settlement agreement for
the uncle's assault case.

54
00:04:45,190 --> 00:04:46,359
Both parties are satisfied.

55
00:04:46,360 --> 00:04:47,960
I don't think they'll go back
on their agreement.

56
00:04:47,960 --> 00:04:49,470
Finally, our efforts are not in vain.

57
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:50,829
Well,

58
00:04:50,830 --> 00:04:51,629
the information

59
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:53,949
on the twins' inheritance case
I asked you to prepare...

60
00:04:53,950 --> 00:04:55,149
I forgot.

61
00:04:55,150 --> 00:04:57,680
Why are you so careless?

62
00:04:58,630 --> 00:04:59,709
Our cases

63
00:04:59,710 --> 00:05:01,479
have been messy ones.

64
00:05:01,480 --> 00:05:03,120
I forgot because I've been busy.

65
00:05:07,510 --> 00:05:09,270
Let me tell you something happy.

66
00:05:09,830 --> 00:05:12,149
I got Feng Shengli's case.

67
00:05:12,150 --> 00:05:13,390
Really?

68
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:14,439
Master.

69
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:17,070
This case is a hot topic
on the internet.

70
00:05:17,120 --> 00:05:18,560
It is very controversial.

71
00:05:18,630 --> 00:05:20,760
What are they talking about?
Which side are they on?

72
00:05:20,920 --> 00:05:22,630
Some people side with the parents

73
00:05:22,830 --> 00:05:24,559
but there are also many people

74
00:05:24,560 --> 00:05:26,800
who support Feng Shengli
in breaking ties with his father.

75
00:05:29,510 --> 00:05:31,560
What values do they have?

76
00:05:32,070 --> 00:05:33,439
I assume

77
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:35,389
they are all young people

78
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:37,389
who came from farming villages
to the city to work.

79
00:05:37,390 --> 00:05:40,000
They understand the difficulty
of a child from a farming village.

80
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,189
People on the internet have been
talking about this in recent years.

81
00:05:42,190 --> 00:05:43,509
I also grew up in the village

82
00:05:43,510 --> 00:05:44,949
and came all the way to the city.

83
00:05:44,950 --> 00:05:45,879
Parents from the village

84
00:05:45,880 --> 00:05:47,679
aren't all the same
as what they see in dramas.

85
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:48,509
In my opinion,

86
00:05:48,510 --> 00:05:51,400
they are just bullying the old folks from
the village for having no access to the internet

87
00:05:51,400 --> 00:05:53,069
so they keep slandering them.

88
00:05:53,070 --> 00:05:54,829
If they say they have a poor background,

89
00:05:54,830 --> 00:05:56,680
they describe it
as something embarrassing.

90
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,629
Once they talk about
parents making requests to children,

91
00:05:58,630 --> 00:06:00,149
they call them self-centered

92
00:06:00,150 --> 00:06:01,679
and being unreasonable.

93
00:06:01,680 --> 00:06:02,559
Su Qi, I'm telling you,

94
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,949
we must deal Feng Shengli's case properly

95
00:06:04,950 --> 00:06:07,039
and turn this value around.

96
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,119
Master.

97
00:06:08,120 --> 00:06:10,269
His father and elder siblings

98
00:06:10,270 --> 00:06:12,479
might have provided him
with a lot of support

99
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,889
but when I think about

100
00:06:13,890 --> 00:06:16,069
how a lad from a village

101
00:06:16,070 --> 00:06:17,239
has to take on the burden

102
00:06:17,240 --> 00:06:19,479
of changing his whole family's lives,

103
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,920
it does make me feel despair.

104
00:06:22,750 --> 00:06:24,590
Su Qi, remember.

105
00:06:25,040 --> 00:06:26,749
From our perspective,

106
00:06:26,750 --> 00:06:28,950
we still need to find out the truth.

107
00:06:29,070 --> 00:06:31,510
Ensure a fair trial,
uninfluenced by public opinion.

108
00:06:31,710 --> 00:06:34,440
Take a clear and resolute stance.

109
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:36,269
At the same time,

110
00:06:36,270 --> 00:06:38,920
we also need
to touch people's hearts with warmth.

111
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,270
Here are your health checkup reports.

112
00:06:42,310 --> 00:06:43,749
Mine.

113
00:06:43,750 --> 00:06:44,799
Let me take a look at mine.

114
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:45,439
This is mine.

115
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,559
This is mine.

116
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,560
This is mine.

117
00:06:49,600 --> 00:06:50,560
Yours.

118
00:06:52,390 --> 00:06:53,919
Why are there so many?

119
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,920
Le, here's yours.

120
00:06:58,560 --> 00:06:59,119
Le.

121
00:06:59,120 --> 00:06:59,799
Thank you.

122
00:06:59,800 --> 00:07:01,799
There's a lump in my breast.

123
00:07:01,800 --> 00:07:05,149
They recommend that I
get an examination at the hospital.

124
00:07:05,150 --> 00:07:05,829
So serious?

125
00:07:05,830 --> 00:07:07,749
Why is yours so serious?

126
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:09,239
Thankfully, mine is only on the left.

127
00:07:09,240 --> 00:07:10,880
I have them on both sides.

128
00:07:13,150 --> 00:07:14,149
Where is Jing's?

129
00:07:14,150 --> 00:07:15,800
I left it on her table.

130
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,840
Look. Le is so calm.

131
00:07:18,840 --> 00:07:19,840
I'm sure she doesn't have any.

132
00:07:19,840 --> 00:07:21,760
Being carefree makes you
free from illnesses indeed.

133
00:07:23,270 --> 00:07:24,949
Remember to keep your morning free

134
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:27,800
for the talk this Friday.

135
00:07:28,310 --> 00:07:29,359
What talk?

136
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,829
An annual talk.

137
00:07:30,830 --> 00:07:32,880
A specialist from the breast department
of the People's Hospital

138
00:07:32,880 --> 00:07:35,560
is coming to give us a talk
on breast care.

139
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,999
Since it's already the truth,

140
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:39,509
what's the use of listening to the talk?

141
00:07:39,510 --> 00:07:42,150
Just go and feel
the organization's care.

142
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,509
Then, everyone will feel better.

143
00:07:44,510 --> 00:07:45,599
Exactly.

144
00:07:45,600 --> 00:07:47,999
Remember to call Shen Xiezhi.

145
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,879
He has been troubled lately.

146
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:52,590
He needs
the organization's care the most.

147
00:07:57,400 --> 00:07:59,559
(Outpatient, People's Hospital)

148
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:00,709
(Breast Department)

149
00:08:00,710 --> 00:08:01,919
It'll be fine.

150
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:04,120
Don't feel pressured.

151
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:06,039
Worst-case scenario,

152
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,879
if the result is positive,

153
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,479
it's nothing much.

154
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,629
We'll just get an expert
to run a detailed examination.

155
00:08:10,630 --> 00:08:12,470
That's easy for you to say.

156
00:08:12,710 --> 00:08:13,559
Remember.

157
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,709
When it comes to breasts,

158
00:08:14,710 --> 00:08:16,799
if you notice symptoms early,
it'll be fine.

159
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:18,069
I'm scared.

160
00:08:18,070 --> 00:08:18,829
Move.

161
00:08:18,830 --> 00:08:20,149
What are you doing?

162
00:08:20,150 --> 00:08:21,709
Sorry.

163
00:08:21,710 --> 00:08:23,829
Mister, why are you running?

164
00:08:23,830 --> 00:08:25,239
We are going to run an examination.

165
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,039
I'm not doing it!

166
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,149
Your son said

167
00:08:28,150 --> 00:08:29,359
he'd surely get the money.

168
00:08:29,360 --> 00:08:30,599
Just get the treatment.

169
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,509
You know nothing.

170
00:08:31,510 --> 00:08:32,679
I'll never do it.

171
00:08:32,680 --> 00:08:33,950
- Mister.
- Go away.

172
00:08:34,720 --> 00:08:35,509
You...

173
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,710
Are you all right?

174
00:08:37,030 --> 00:08:38,269
Thank you.

175
00:08:38,270 --> 00:08:40,029
You're as strong as a donkey.

176
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:41,680
You don't look like you have uremia.

177
00:08:42,030 --> 00:08:42,950
Sorry.

178
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:47,429
Feng Jianye,

179
00:08:47,430 --> 00:08:49,319
your father escaped again.

180
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:51,070
I can't do anything.

181
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:53,479
All of you should contact him.

182
00:08:53,480 --> 00:08:54,079
Please wait.

183
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:56,350
Why don't you handle his discharge?

184
00:08:56,430 --> 00:08:59,239
Sure. I'll go and take care
of other patients first.

185
00:08:59,240 --> 00:08:59,839
Hello.

186
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:02,280
Was that man called Feng Lianshan?

187
00:09:02,390 --> 00:09:03,789
Yes. Do you know him?

188
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:05,839
Doesn't he have late-stage uremia?
How can he still run around?

189
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:07,239
Neither the glomerular filtration rate

190
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,669
nor the endogenous creatinine clearance

191
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:10,800
has been tested.

192
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,319
He just won't cooperate with us.

193
00:09:12,320 --> 00:09:15,400
It doesn't seem like
there's anything wrong with him.

194
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:19,710
Danian,

195
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:21,230
let's go.

196
00:09:30,430 --> 00:09:31,879
Dad, you should have one.

197
00:09:31,880 --> 00:09:32,789
Sure.

198
00:09:32,790 --> 00:09:33,719
Eat.

199
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,870
See if the grape is sweet. Tell me.

200
00:09:42,510 --> 00:09:44,200
Why are you staring at me?

201
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:57,719
Su Qi.

202
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,239
Regarding Feng Shengli's case,

203
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,839
you should hurry up
and arrange the documents.

204
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:02,749
Especially his father's

205
00:10:02,750 --> 00:10:04,141
medical reports.

206
00:10:04,142 --> 00:10:05,839
I'll go back and deal with the rest.

207
00:10:05,840 --> 00:10:06,719
All right.

208
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,640
All right.

209
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:11,199
Do you think his uremia is fake?

210
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,359
No.

211
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:13,749
Perhaps he's not

212
00:10:13,750 --> 00:10:16,199
pretending to be sick
but afraid of spending money instead.

213
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:17,199
That's impossible.

214
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:20,060
At this stage, do you think he's still scared of
spending some money on an examination?

215
00:10:20,060 --> 00:10:21,319
Besides, you saw it today.

216
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,029
His strength

217
00:10:22,030 --> 00:10:23,870
was enough to knock both of us over.

218
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:26,440
- Do you think it really is uremia?
- Indeed.

219
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:29,400
Who knows?
It has nothing to do with me.

220
00:10:39,910 --> 00:10:41,599
You look like you're in a rush.
Where are you going?

221
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,680
I'm going to the police station
to investigate a household.

222
00:10:43,910 --> 00:10:46,079
How many places are you going to?
When are you coming back?

223
00:10:46,080 --> 00:10:47,669
If nothing goes wrong,

224
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:49,350
I won't be back for lunch.

225
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:52,029
I'm sure it's tough working alone.

226
00:10:52,030 --> 00:10:53,789
Should I get someone else
to go with you?

227
00:10:53,790 --> 00:10:54,789
Sure.

228
00:10:54,790 --> 00:10:56,640
Let me ask if Hu Aixi is free.

229
00:10:56,880 --> 00:10:57,599
Forget about it.

230
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,549
I still have a few court cases
to attend to the whole day.

231
00:10:59,550 --> 00:11:00,999
Who else is free now?

232
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:02,749
I've seen the schedule
on the blackboard.

233
00:11:02,750 --> 00:11:04,440
Everyone's schedule is full today.

234
00:11:04,720 --> 00:11:07,520
Think about the people
whose names are not on the blackboard.

235
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,909
This is an external investigation
and not a court trial.

236
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:11,230
It's not against the rule.

237
00:11:11,390 --> 00:11:12,470
Sure.

238
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:13,950
Ms. Shu, don't worry.

239
00:11:14,270 --> 00:11:16,160
Although memorizing the law
is difficult for me,

240
00:11:16,270 --> 00:11:17,079
comforting friends,

241
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:18,719
telling jokes, and lifting the mood

242
00:11:18,720 --> 00:11:20,200
are what I'm good at.

243
00:11:31,910 --> 00:11:33,350
Be separated and calm down.

244
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:43,710
Awarded to the mother.

245
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:57,959
This is a Pixiu.

246
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:59,320
It has a mouth
and doesn't have an anus.

247
00:11:59,320 --> 00:12:00,960
It swallows everything
without leaking anything.

248
00:12:00,960 --> 00:12:03,800
It eats all things with nothing going out,
so it gathers fortune.

249
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:05,719
Do you want to buy one

250
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:06,599
and place it in your home

251
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:08,440
for good fortune and luck?

252
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,920
Sure.

253
00:12:10,200 --> 00:12:11,119
Wrap it up for me.

254
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,280
All right.

255
00:12:20,340 --> 00:12:21,150
Hello.

256
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,999
- What's wrong?
- I have some external investigation work.

257
00:12:24,000 --> 00:12:25,719
Ms. Shu is worried about me going alone

258
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:27,350
so she asked me
to get someone to go with me.

259
00:12:27,670 --> 00:12:29,870
Mr. He asked me
not to go to the court recently.

260
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:31,999
I'm not asking you
to come to the court.

261
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,669
It's an external investigation.

262
00:12:33,670 --> 00:12:34,990
We are going outside to investigate.

263
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:39,669
Sure.

264
00:12:39,670 --> 00:12:41,509
I'm at the Bairun Commercial Street.

265
00:12:41,510 --> 00:12:42,920
Come and pick me up.

266
00:12:43,480 --> 00:12:44,909
I can't pick you up.

267
00:12:44,910 --> 00:12:46,590
Every court vehicle has been dispatched.

268
00:12:46,790 --> 00:12:48,160
I'll hail a ride to pick you up.

269
00:12:48,390 --> 00:12:50,870
If you are driving,
why don't you pick me up instead?

270
00:12:52,720 --> 00:12:54,920
Fine. I'll come and pick you up.

271
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,509
I'll drive up to the court

272
00:12:56,510 --> 00:12:57,509
without going inside.

273
00:12:57,510 --> 00:12:59,200
Okay. See you later.

274
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:00,800
All right.

275
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,429
Sorry.

276
00:13:03,430 --> 00:13:05,359
I have something to tell you.

277
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,429
What you were looking at

278
00:13:06,430 --> 00:13:08,120
wasn't a Pixiu but a Xiezhi.
[* A mythical beast.]

279
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:10,079
The Pixiu's leg goes backwards.

280
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:11,629
The Xiezhi's leg goes forward.

281
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:13,079
I didn't recognize it just now.

282
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,269
This is the Pixiu.

283
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:16,640
Why don't you choose again?

284
00:13:17,960 --> 00:13:19,400
It's fine. I want this.

285
00:13:19,728 --> 00:13:20,669
No.

286
00:13:20,670 --> 00:13:22,029
This Xiezhi

287
00:13:22,030 --> 00:13:23,079
has its horn damaged

288
00:13:23,080 --> 00:13:25,710
by some uncivilized person.

289
00:13:25,790 --> 00:13:27,119
Without its horn,

290
00:13:27,120 --> 00:13:28,669
can it still be called a Xiezhi?

291
00:13:28,670 --> 00:13:30,629
I wanted to get you a new one

292
00:13:30,630 --> 00:13:31,870
but

293
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:33,920
this is the last one in our shop.

294
00:13:42,750 --> 00:13:44,590
It's fine. I'll take this.

295
00:13:44,960 --> 00:13:46,230
It shares

296
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,830
the same fate as me.

297
00:13:48,360 --> 00:13:49,319
Wrap it up.

298
00:13:49,320 --> 00:13:50,800
Brother!

299
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:53,830
Rest in peace, Brother!

300
00:13:57,430 --> 00:13:59,149
The one who makes the decision,
come and talk to me.

301
00:13:59,150 --> 00:14:00,479
The court has killed someone

302
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:02,230
without giving an explanation until now.

303
00:14:02,270 --> 00:14:05,280
All of you are just covering each other.

304
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:08,280
- What's going on? It's so noisy.
- I guess someone died in court.

305
00:14:08,320 --> 00:14:09,440
Is that so?

306
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:11,549
Take note. Jindian Law Firm

307
00:14:11,550 --> 00:14:12,509
is just across the road.

308
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:15,149
You couldn't even rest in peace.

309
00:14:15,150 --> 00:14:17,719
They opened you up

310
00:14:17,720 --> 00:14:19,429
with your guts all over the ground.

311
00:14:19,430 --> 00:14:21,359
Come and find me
if you have any legal questions.

312
00:14:21,360 --> 00:14:22,950
Free consultation.

313
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:24,350
Mister.

314
00:14:24,390 --> 00:14:25,359
What's going on?

315
00:14:25,360 --> 00:14:27,599
I think the court
caused an old man's death.

316
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:29,359
It's related to a corrupt judge.

317
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:30,669
I don't believe you.

318
00:14:30,670 --> 00:14:32,029
Shen Xiezhi!

319
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:35,040
(Judge Shen, that's impossible.)

320
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,920
You must assert your rights lawfully and
not interfere with the order of the court.

321
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:39,549
He's already dead!

322
00:14:39,550 --> 00:14:41,710
How are we going
to live the rest of our lives?

323
00:14:41,790 --> 00:14:43,079
Who's in charge?

324
00:14:43,080 --> 00:14:45,200
Come out and say something!

325
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:47,429
Ms. Shu,

326
00:14:47,430 --> 00:14:49,590
Mr. Yao's family
is causing trouble outside the court.

327
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,959
They are making it look like a funeral.

328
00:14:51,960 --> 00:14:53,509
Mr. Huang brought someone with him
to stop them.

329
00:14:53,510 --> 00:14:54,830
He told me to come find you.

330
00:14:54,910 --> 00:14:55,950
Let's go.

331
00:14:56,360 --> 00:14:57,789
Ms. Shu, let me go with you.

332
00:14:57,790 --> 00:14:59,680
Send the court trial notice first.

333
00:15:06,840 --> 00:15:07,959
Go down. I'll go downstairs soon.

334
00:15:07,960 --> 00:15:09,110
All right.

335
00:15:10,910 --> 00:15:12,160
Chen Xianghui.

336
00:15:12,550 --> 00:15:14,440
Is Shen Xiezhi picking you up?

337
00:15:14,480 --> 00:15:15,990
He's at the court entrance?

338
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:18,560
Take him away
from the court immediately.

339
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:20,149
Shen Xiezhi!

340
00:15:20,150 --> 00:15:21,830
Come out!

341
00:15:21,960 --> 00:15:23,870
Return my brother to me!

342
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:25,710
Come out!

343
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,870
Return my brother to me!

344
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:33,029
What's wrong?

345
00:15:33,030 --> 00:15:34,269
All of them are here to find you.

346
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,640
Find me?

347
00:15:36,840 --> 00:15:38,640
Shen Xiezhi, come out!

348
00:15:38,790 --> 00:15:39,879
Come out!

349
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:41,400
Come out!

350
00:15:44,600 --> 00:15:45,599
You can't go there.

351
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:46,509
Why not?

352
00:15:46,510 --> 00:15:47,509
I'll go and talk to them.

353
00:15:47,510 --> 00:15:48,870
It'll be a mess.

354
00:15:54,480 --> 00:15:55,509
Why are you here?

355
00:15:55,510 --> 00:15:57,280
Ms. Shu asked me to keep an eye on you.

356
00:15:58,750 --> 00:16:01,149
I can't hide from this forever.

357
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:02,600
Let me go
and make things clear with them.

358
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,710
No. Calm down.

359
00:16:04,910 --> 00:16:06,509
Shen Xiezhi!

360
00:16:06,510 --> 00:16:08,239
If you are not guilty,

361
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:10,640
why are you avoiding us?

362
00:16:11,000 --> 00:16:12,350
Come out!

363
00:16:13,120 --> 00:16:14,029
Do you hear that?

364
00:16:14,030 --> 00:16:16,389
They are already saying that.
More reason for me to go there.

365
00:16:16,390 --> 00:16:18,359
You are being suspended
and investigated right now.

366
00:16:18,360 --> 00:16:19,839
Going there will only make things worse.

367
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:21,479
Let Ms. Shu deal with it for now.

368
00:16:21,480 --> 00:16:22,669
Mr. Chen.

369
00:16:22,670 --> 00:16:23,359
Ms. Qin.

370
00:16:23,360 --> 00:16:24,429
Judge Shen, you're here, too?

371
00:16:24,430 --> 00:16:25,719
It's quite a mess over there.

372
00:16:25,720 --> 00:16:27,590
I think they are against Judge Shen.

373
00:16:28,150 --> 00:16:30,389
Do you need me to do anything?

374
00:16:30,390 --> 00:16:31,789
Can you ask the car behind to move?

375
00:16:31,790 --> 00:16:33,119
We need to back away.

376
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:33,959
Sure.

377
00:16:33,960 --> 00:16:35,040
Thank you.

378
00:16:35,150 --> 00:16:35,879
Hello.

379
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:36,789
Excuse me, Sir.

380
00:16:36,790 --> 00:16:37,549
What's wrong, Hui?

381
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:38,509
Ask the cars behind to move.

382
00:16:38,510 --> 00:16:39,269
- Sure.
- My colleague is in front.

383
00:16:39,270 --> 00:16:40,920
They want to back away.
Can you move backwards?

384
00:16:42,510 --> 00:16:44,160
Come out!

385
00:16:44,600 --> 00:16:46,749
Return my brother to me!

386
00:16:46,750 --> 00:16:48,719
Come out and give us an explanation!

387
00:16:48,720 --> 00:16:50,269
Shen Xiezhi!

388
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:51,950
Come out!

389
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:52,879
They've reversed the car.

390
00:16:52,880 --> 00:16:53,999
Where are you guys going?

391
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:54,879
You should get on.

392
00:16:54,880 --> 00:16:56,040
Sure.

393
00:16:56,200 --> 00:16:57,879
Why are you getting a lawyer?
I'll go and talk to them.

394
00:16:57,880 --> 00:16:59,590
Listen to me.
We should first leave this place.

395
00:17:34,040 --> 00:17:35,550
I'm just like a criminal.

396
00:17:36,990 --> 00:17:38,270
Judge Shen,

397
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:39,519
I think

398
00:17:39,520 --> 00:17:41,680
you don't need to take this to heart.

399
00:17:41,800 --> 00:17:43,510
They're all worked up right now,

400
00:17:43,710 --> 00:17:45,270
so they're bound to be emotional.

401
00:17:46,390 --> 00:17:47,510
But

402
00:17:47,520 --> 00:17:48,920
no matter what,

403
00:17:49,190 --> 00:17:51,470
I believe
that you're not that kind of person.

404
00:17:53,990 --> 00:17:55,400
Thank you.

405
00:17:55,560 --> 00:17:57,160
You are quite experienced.

406
00:17:58,120 --> 00:17:59,759
Not really.

407
00:17:59,760 --> 00:18:01,790
It's just an observation.

408
00:18:02,080 --> 00:18:03,790
I'm in front
of the court entrance every day.

409
00:18:03,800 --> 00:18:06,120
I've seen all kinds of people
and all sorts of things.

410
00:18:24,990 --> 00:18:26,599
Thank you, Ms. Qin.

411
00:18:26,600 --> 00:18:27,389
Not at all.

412
00:18:27,390 --> 00:18:29,189
Why don't you come inside
and have a drink?

413
00:18:29,190 --> 00:18:30,879
Since you're here,
come inside and warm up.

414
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:31,629
Those people over there

415
00:18:31,630 --> 00:18:33,039
won't be leaving soon.

416
00:18:33,040 --> 00:18:34,840
A judge won't take a drink
offered by a lawyer.

417
00:18:43,040 --> 00:18:44,709
Judge Shen and I still need to go
for an external investigation.

418
00:18:44,710 --> 00:18:47,319
I'll take a detour later
and not pass by the court entrance.

419
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:48,640
Thank you, Ms. Qin.

420
00:18:49,390 --> 00:18:51,710
Both of you, thank you.
You may get back to work.

421
00:18:52,390 --> 00:18:53,840
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

422
00:19:00,080 --> 00:19:01,680
My kindness is in vain.

423
00:19:03,390 --> 00:19:05,519
Your behavior
is a disruption to public order.

424
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:07,550
You need to assert your rights
through legal and proper means.

425
00:19:07,950 --> 00:19:10,039
We will inform you immediately
once the test results are out.

426
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:11,230
All right?

427
00:19:12,600 --> 00:19:14,470
I... I'm not going against the law.

428
00:19:14,760 --> 00:19:17,790
We are not together.

429
00:19:21,800 --> 00:19:23,879
Previously, I heard them say

430
00:19:23,880 --> 00:19:26,710
that keyboard malfunctions
are common in objective question exams.

431
00:19:26,910 --> 00:19:27,989
I figured

432
00:19:27,990 --> 00:19:30,270
I'd press every button once

433
00:19:30,280 --> 00:19:31,669
and if any of them didn't work,

434
00:19:31,670 --> 00:19:33,270
I'd ask the invigilator to change it.

435
00:19:33,950 --> 00:19:35,750
In the end, I pressed a key

436
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:37,319
that quits the system.

437
00:19:37,320 --> 00:19:38,750
It was even stuck.

438
00:19:43,520 --> 00:19:44,389
(Shu Jing: Are you in the car?)

439
00:19:44,390 --> 00:19:45,990
Where was I?

440
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:48,519
The system quit itself
and got stuck, right?

441
00:19:48,520 --> 00:19:50,189
I called the invigilator

442
00:19:50,190 --> 00:19:51,559
but he didn't know what to do.

443
00:19:51,560 --> 00:19:53,120
He went and found an old man.

444
00:19:53,320 --> 00:19:55,519
We tried to solve it until ten seconds
before the exam began.

445
00:19:55,520 --> 00:19:57,389
Here's the critical thing.

446
00:19:57,390 --> 00:19:58,319
I didn't get

447
00:19:58,320 --> 00:20:00,310
to test the space bar.

448
00:20:00,470 --> 00:20:02,440
That space bar was stuck.

449
00:20:03,080 --> 00:20:04,599
Can you imagine the feeling

450
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:05,669
of crazily pressing the space bar

451
00:20:05,670 --> 00:20:07,360
every time I typed a word?

452
00:20:07,670 --> 00:20:08,599
Judge Shen,

453
00:20:08,600 --> 00:20:10,149
am I unlucky or what?

454
00:20:10,150 --> 00:20:11,320
(Jiang Feng: I'm filing for divorce at
the Civil Affairs Bureau. Pick me up.)

455
00:20:11,320 --> 00:20:11,760
(Shen Xiezhi: Ok.)

456
00:20:15,760 --> 00:20:18,160
Drop me off
at the subway station in front.

457
00:20:20,560 --> 00:20:22,039
If you think I'm annoying,

458
00:20:22,040 --> 00:20:23,469
I can shut up.

459
00:20:23,470 --> 00:20:24,680
No.

460
00:20:24,950 --> 00:20:26,710
I know all of you care about me

461
00:20:26,910 --> 00:20:29,030
but I'm being suspended right now.

462
00:20:29,120 --> 00:20:31,470
Before the final investigation result is out,

463
00:20:32,840 --> 00:20:34,599
I should stay away from the court

464
00:20:34,600 --> 00:20:36,160
so I won't be caught by others

465
00:20:36,190 --> 00:20:38,190
and end up causing
unnecessary trouble for all of you.

466
00:20:38,191 --> 00:20:39,519
Judge Shen,

467
00:20:39,520 --> 00:20:41,680
I think you don't need
to be so stubborn on things.

468
00:20:45,470 --> 00:20:47,440
I should send you home instead.

469
00:20:49,230 --> 00:20:50,440
No need.

470
00:20:50,600 --> 00:20:51,949
Just drive my car back

471
00:20:51,950 --> 00:20:54,160
and drop me at the subway station.

472
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:56,629
I've contacted Jiang Feng.

473
00:20:56,630 --> 00:20:58,030
I'm going to see him.

474
00:20:58,670 --> 00:21:00,920
Tell Jing not to worry about me.

475
00:21:01,190 --> 00:21:02,400
All right.

476
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:11,480
(Qingcheng District
Civil Affairs Bureau, Tianhai City)

477
00:21:33,120 --> 00:21:34,270
Where are you?

478
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:36,000
Beside you.

479
00:21:37,160 --> 00:21:40,559
(Divorce Registration)

480
00:21:40,560 --> 00:21:42,360
(Qingcheng Tianhai Civil Affairs Bureau,
Marriage Registration)

481
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:48,120
(Marriage Registration)

482
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:55,839
What's the meaning of this?

483
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:58,510
You are filing for divorce.
Why are you sitting here?

484
00:21:59,390 --> 00:22:01,160
The air conditioning
is too cold over there.

485
00:22:01,840 --> 00:22:03,270
It makes people feel despair.

486
00:22:05,630 --> 00:22:06,920
Right.

487
00:22:07,390 --> 00:22:09,470
This place is warm and comforting.

488
00:22:09,760 --> 00:22:12,360
The real feel temperature is two degrees warmer
than the opposite place.

489
00:22:12,630 --> 00:22:15,030
It gets rid of
your negativity for the whole month.

490
00:22:16,080 --> 00:22:17,189
A good place.

491
00:22:17,190 --> 00:22:19,600
Come here often
if you're in a bad mood next time.

492
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,950
You are a family court judge...

493
00:22:24,600 --> 00:22:26,360
So what?

494
00:22:26,800 --> 00:22:27,709
Yes.

495
00:22:27,710 --> 00:22:29,389
You always see robbery and murder

496
00:22:29,390 --> 00:22:31,599
at the criminal court.

497
00:22:31,600 --> 00:22:33,989
The visual impact is stronger
than on my side

498
00:22:33,990 --> 00:22:34,629
but

499
00:22:34,630 --> 00:22:37,400
if the suspect and evidence
are both irrefutable,

500
00:22:37,430 --> 00:22:39,440
you just need to give out
the sentence according to the law.

501
00:22:39,470 --> 00:22:40,629
The family court

502
00:22:40,630 --> 00:22:43,079
is where family members
go against each other.

503
00:22:43,080 --> 00:22:44,359
They use the harshest words

504
00:22:44,360 --> 00:22:45,949
to hurt the person
they used to love most.

505
00:22:45,950 --> 00:22:46,599
In the end,

506
00:22:46,600 --> 00:22:49,119
the passion ends up
having nowhere to go.

507
00:22:49,120 --> 00:22:50,599
I am caught in between

508
00:22:50,600 --> 00:22:52,429
and am buried in

509
00:22:52,430 --> 00:22:53,839
all sorts of emotions.

510
00:22:53,840 --> 00:22:55,160
No matter what I do,

511
00:22:55,230 --> 00:22:57,680
I won't achieve a perfect result.

512
00:23:01,430 --> 00:23:03,790
That's enough, Brother.
You don't need to do this.

513
00:23:04,430 --> 00:23:05,839
If you want to become a machine,

514
00:23:05,840 --> 00:23:07,640
you need to act like one.

515
00:23:07,670 --> 00:23:09,600
Let go of your sorrow.

516
00:23:09,630 --> 00:23:11,200
According to the procedures,

517
00:23:12,080 --> 00:23:13,469
you should comfort me.

518
00:23:13,470 --> 00:23:14,680
That's right.

519
00:23:16,120 --> 00:23:17,400
Sorry.

520
00:23:19,120 --> 00:23:21,949
It's pretty tragic that love falls apart
and the family breaks up.

521
00:23:21,950 --> 00:23:24,200
Are you still holding up well,
my buddy?

522
00:23:24,390 --> 00:23:26,839
What? Are you looking down on
someone whose marriage failed?

523
00:23:26,840 --> 00:23:28,470
I dare not.

524
00:23:28,600 --> 00:23:29,680
Come. Let's go eat.

525
00:23:29,710 --> 00:23:31,519
Let's have a drink today.

526
00:23:31,520 --> 00:23:33,120
The rules say

527
00:23:33,560 --> 00:23:34,709
we shouldn't drink.

528
00:23:34,710 --> 00:23:36,120
Well,

529
00:23:36,460 --> 00:23:39,200
aren't you suspended,
and I'm on holiday?

530
00:23:46,520 --> 00:23:48,360
(Jindian Law Firm)

531
00:23:54,990 --> 00:23:56,429
Today, in Rui's Legal Lens,

532
00:23:56,430 --> 00:23:58,079
we won't be talking about cases.

533
00:23:58,080 --> 00:24:00,879
We'll talk about
the most aggrieved moments in life.

534
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:02,039
I know every line of work

535
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:03,550
has such moments.

536
00:24:04,860 --> 00:24:10,690
♪When a leaf can't find a place to fall♪

537
00:24:11,870 --> 00:24:13,459
♪Just like me♪

538
00:24:13,460 --> 00:24:16,840
♪Wandering without a destination♪

539
00:24:18,933 --> 00:24:24,693
♪Until you appear and I see your eyes♪

540
00:24:26,040 --> 00:24:30,880
♪I've decided to stay by your side♪

541
00:24:32,700 --> 00:24:36,509
♪I want to be in your world♪

542
00:24:36,510 --> 00:24:40,100
♪Everything is no longer faraway♪

543
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:42,760
(Divorce Certificate)

544
00:25:04,020 --> 00:25:05,119
Hello.

545
00:25:05,120 --> 00:25:06,669
When are you coming back?

546
00:25:06,670 --> 00:25:09,429
We have meat to eat
in the next few days.

547
00:25:09,430 --> 00:25:10,629
Deboned meat.

548
00:25:10,630 --> 00:25:11,629
(Rui)

549
00:25:11,630 --> 00:25:13,920
I just recorded a video
for my public account.

550
00:25:14,430 --> 00:25:15,429
Well,

551
00:25:15,430 --> 00:25:17,909
fewer people are outside
and I have less work to do at night.

552
00:25:17,910 --> 00:25:19,920
It's quieter so I can record the video.

553
00:25:20,840 --> 00:25:22,149
I just recorded the video once.

554
00:25:22,150 --> 00:25:24,400
I'll go back after I do another one.

555
00:25:24,430 --> 00:25:26,920
Hurry up. I have good news.

556
00:25:27,040 --> 00:25:28,359
What good news

557
00:25:28,360 --> 00:25:29,559
is better than me making money

558
00:25:29,560 --> 00:25:31,319
to help pay your rent?

559
00:25:31,320 --> 00:25:33,790
Of course, it's something
to help make money.

560
00:25:34,190 --> 00:25:35,189
Two days ago,

561
00:25:35,190 --> 00:25:37,039
my father recommended a Madam Xue

562
00:25:37,040 --> 00:25:39,080
to us for handwriting analysis.

563
00:25:40,040 --> 00:25:43,759
Recently, she has
a three-million-yuan copyright case,

564
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:45,270
and she needs a lawyer.

565
00:25:45,320 --> 00:25:48,079
As if that kind of wealth
would ever come my way.

566
00:25:48,080 --> 00:25:49,920
Let me finish.

567
00:25:49,990 --> 00:25:51,310
She said

568
00:25:51,670 --> 00:25:52,909
she doesn't want old lawyers

569
00:25:52,910 --> 00:25:54,600
because they might be slow
on the latest information,

570
00:25:54,600 --> 00:25:55,989
and she doesn't want male lawyers.

571
00:25:55,990 --> 00:25:56,909
I guess

572
00:25:56,910 --> 00:25:57,989
she was somehow hurt

573
00:25:57,990 --> 00:25:59,429
by her ex-husband.

574
00:25:59,430 --> 00:26:01,470
Anyway, I recommended you to her.

575
00:26:01,840 --> 00:26:05,310
I said you were young, sharp,

576
00:26:05,600 --> 00:26:08,279
hardworking, and kept up with the times.

577
00:26:08,280 --> 00:26:10,039
Indeed. We can't compete in other aspects

578
00:26:10,040 --> 00:26:12,319
but we are young and energetic.

579
00:26:12,320 --> 00:26:13,149
Don't worry.

580
00:26:13,150 --> 00:26:15,119
I'll go back later
and brush up on my copyright law.

581
00:26:15,120 --> 00:26:16,429
Next, I'll rent my battle suit.

582
00:26:16,430 --> 00:26:18,030
I'll surely get the case tomorrow.

583
00:26:18,470 --> 00:26:19,600
Be quick.

584
00:26:21,910 --> 00:26:24,880
I'll just leave the bone for myself.

585
00:26:36,840 --> 00:26:37,990
Mister,

586
00:26:38,600 --> 00:26:41,710
just drop me on the side in front.

587
00:26:58,607 --> 00:27:05,167
(Jindian Law Firm)

588
00:27:06,080 --> 00:27:07,149
(I...)

589
00:27:07,150 --> 00:27:08,189
(Why am I back here?)

590
00:27:08,190 --> 00:27:09,629
That's using me.

591
00:27:09,630 --> 00:27:11,079
Did I take a shortcut through you?

592
00:27:11,080 --> 00:27:13,039
If you come to me,
you are bribing the judge.

593
00:27:13,040 --> 00:27:14,909
If you don't, that's fraud.

594
00:27:14,910 --> 00:27:16,840
A judge won't take a drink
offered by a lawyer.

595
00:27:27,230 --> 00:27:28,950
There's only one word for this.

596
00:27:29,520 --> 00:27:30,790
Charisma.

597
00:27:36,190 --> 00:27:37,400
Qin Rui.

598
00:27:38,360 --> 00:27:40,550
Qin Rui, come out!

599
00:27:43,190 --> 00:27:44,669
What are you doing?

600
00:27:44,670 --> 00:27:45,559
I've told you

601
00:27:45,560 --> 00:27:47,079
not to step onto my turf.

602
00:27:47,080 --> 00:27:49,680
I'm drunk.

603
00:27:50,320 --> 00:27:52,359
A judge who drinks?

604
00:27:52,360 --> 00:27:53,839
How many dishes? You seem so drunk.

605
00:27:53,840 --> 00:27:56,229
I... I'm here

606
00:27:56,230 --> 00:27:57,880
to apologize to you.

607
00:27:58,230 --> 00:28:00,709
Sorry for what happened during the day.

608
00:28:00,710 --> 00:28:02,079
Let me apologize to you instead.

609
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:04,189
I just look like a fool

610
00:28:04,190 --> 00:28:06,669
who can't win a case, right?

611
00:28:06,670 --> 00:28:07,950
Don't...

612
00:28:07,990 --> 00:28:09,149
Don't say that.

613
00:28:09,150 --> 00:28:10,669
Don't touch me, I'm telling you.

614
00:28:10,670 --> 00:28:11,839
You are a judge.

615
00:28:11,840 --> 00:28:13,270
I'll record you on a video.

616
00:28:13,360 --> 00:28:14,359
- Show me your face.
- Stop...

617
00:28:14,360 --> 00:28:15,669
Let's take a selfie.

618
00:28:15,670 --> 00:28:17,759
Everyone, look at this.

619
00:28:17,760 --> 00:28:18,839
This is Judge Shen Xiezhi.

620
00:28:18,840 --> 00:28:20,519
He is the one

621
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:22,189
bother me today.

622
00:28:22,190 --> 00:28:23,599
I'm recording this as evidence.

623
00:28:23,600 --> 00:28:25,030
See?

624
00:28:32,320 --> 00:28:34,080
Shen Xiezhi.

625
00:28:53,120 --> 00:28:54,440
What's that smell?

626
00:28:54,670 --> 00:28:56,030
Did you drink?

627
00:28:56,630 --> 00:28:58,310
Shen Xiezhi drank.

628
00:28:58,760 --> 00:29:00,550
Shen Xiezhi drank?

629
00:29:00,990 --> 00:29:02,200
What?

630
00:29:02,230 --> 00:29:03,600
Did he throw up on you?

631
00:29:05,320 --> 00:29:06,469
Go and wash the outfit.

632
00:29:06,470 --> 00:29:07,429
You have to wear it tomorrow.

633
00:29:07,430 --> 00:29:08,149
Hurry up.

634
00:29:08,150 --> 00:29:10,680
There's no use.

635
00:29:11,080 --> 00:29:12,429
It's everywhere.

636
00:29:12,430 --> 00:29:13,469
Look how bad it is.

637
00:29:13,470 --> 00:29:14,990
It can't be cleaned.

638
00:29:17,990 --> 00:29:19,519
Should I just wear this

639
00:29:19,520 --> 00:29:20,839
and meet the client with you tomorrow?

640
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:22,319
I won't embarrass you, right?

641
00:29:22,320 --> 00:29:24,559
I don't mind, of course.

642
00:29:24,560 --> 00:29:27,120
I just go everywhere with my white robe.

643
00:29:27,230 --> 00:29:29,879
I'm just worried that Madam Xue

644
00:29:29,880 --> 00:29:31,189
might be difficult to deal with.

645
00:29:31,190 --> 00:29:32,559
Doesn't she

646
00:29:32,560 --> 00:29:34,279
do things unconventionally?

647
00:29:34,280 --> 00:29:36,879
She's not even
using the famous law firm

648
00:29:36,880 --> 00:29:38,469
or a famous lawyer.

649
00:29:38,470 --> 00:29:40,189
She also didn't care
if I was experienced or not.

650
00:29:40,190 --> 00:29:42,120
I'll tell you honestly.

651
00:29:42,670 --> 00:29:44,920
What she said that day was...

652
00:29:44,950 --> 00:29:47,189
I don't want lawyers
who wear suits and ties.

653
00:29:47,190 --> 00:29:48,319
She thinks

654
00:29:48,320 --> 00:29:49,759
all excellent lawyers

655
00:29:49,760 --> 00:29:51,709
are well-informed
and highly experienced.

656
00:29:51,710 --> 00:29:53,989
So, for a case
like intellectual property,

657
00:29:53,990 --> 00:29:55,559
you need to look the part.

658
00:29:55,560 --> 00:29:57,149
Look the part?

659
00:29:57,150 --> 00:29:58,599
I just need to win the case for her.

660
00:29:58,600 --> 00:29:59,709
That's all.

661
00:29:59,710 --> 00:30:01,440
Does she watch too many movies?

662
00:30:02,080 --> 00:30:05,120
She is not reasonable.

663
00:30:05,150 --> 00:30:06,640
Then...

664
00:30:06,760 --> 00:30:08,710
I can't rent anything else at this time.

665
00:30:09,670 --> 00:30:11,080
Why don't you

666
00:30:11,112 --> 00:30:13,149
tell her to delay the meeting

667
00:30:13,150 --> 00:30:14,319
tomorrow?

668
00:30:14,320 --> 00:30:15,519
I'll think of something.

669
00:30:15,520 --> 00:30:17,319
I'll find a platform
that rents outfits in the morning.

670
00:30:17,320 --> 00:30:18,909
Go and find an outfit rental platform

671
00:30:18,910 --> 00:30:20,510
that delivers in the morning.

672
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:22,319
I just don't know if they can make it.

673
00:30:22,320 --> 00:30:23,510
It's too early.

674
00:30:25,200 --> 00:30:28,720
(Outfit Rental)

675
00:30:29,600 --> 00:30:30,949
You haven't told me

676
00:30:30,950 --> 00:30:33,310
why Shen Xiezhi threw up on you.

677
00:30:34,710 --> 00:30:36,400
He probably likes me.

678
00:30:37,080 --> 00:30:39,200
He wants to buy me a new outfit
but is too embarrassed to tell me.

679
00:30:43,650 --> 00:30:49,490
♪When a leaf can't find a place to fall♪

680
00:30:50,730 --> 00:30:52,319
♪Just like me♪

681
00:30:52,320 --> 00:30:55,840
♪Wandering without a destination♪

682
00:30:57,770 --> 00:31:03,540
♪Until you appear and I see your eyes♪

683
00:31:04,860 --> 00:31:09,700
♪I've decided to stay by your side♪

684
00:31:11,710 --> 00:31:13,229
What are you doing?

685
00:31:13,230 --> 00:31:13,949
I've told you

686
00:31:13,950 --> 00:31:15,920
not to step onto my turf.

687
00:31:16,880 --> 00:31:17,879
(Qin Rui?)

688
00:31:17,880 --> 00:31:19,319
(Why did I go find her?)

689
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:20,669
Don't touch me, I'm telling you.

690
00:31:20,670 --> 00:31:21,909
You are a judge.

691
00:31:21,910 --> 00:31:23,360
I'll record you on a video.

692
00:31:29,150 --> 00:31:30,599
If I didn't get the case

693
00:31:30,600 --> 00:31:31,759
because of this outfit,

694
00:31:31,760 --> 00:31:33,440
you must compensate me!

695
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:36,400
(I spoiled her outfit?)

696
00:31:37,240 --> 00:31:41,839
(Law brings order to the world,
Virtue nurtures the human heart)

697
00:31:41,840 --> 00:31:44,710
I've been advising
for more than an hour.

698
00:31:44,800 --> 00:31:46,880
Give me some reaction, at least.

699
00:31:47,190 --> 00:31:48,909
All of you are siblings.

700
00:31:48,910 --> 00:31:51,550
Can't you just discuss things openly?

701
00:31:52,080 --> 00:31:53,680
Our condition remains the same.

702
00:31:53,840 --> 00:31:55,149
Get him to test his kidneys

703
00:31:55,150 --> 00:31:56,709
and see if they are
compatible with my father.

704
00:31:56,710 --> 00:31:58,039
Impossible.

705
00:31:58,040 --> 00:31:59,279
I'll compensate in the form of money

706
00:31:59,280 --> 00:32:00,680
but asking for my kidney is impossible.

707
00:32:00,910 --> 00:32:03,149
I can responsibly tell you

708
00:32:03,150 --> 00:32:05,229
that if this goes to a court trial,

709
00:32:05,230 --> 00:32:06,429
the result is obvious.

710
00:32:06,430 --> 00:32:08,470
He just needs
to pay for maintenance, at most.

711
00:32:08,990 --> 00:32:12,229
Whether he donates his kidney or not
is his right as a citizen.

712
00:32:12,230 --> 00:32:13,799
The court can't force him to do that.

713
00:32:13,800 --> 00:32:16,149
Just like how the court can't force you
to donate your kidney.

714
00:32:16,150 --> 00:32:17,599
I'm sure you understand that.

715
00:32:17,600 --> 00:32:19,160
Then, my dad can't be saved.

716
00:32:19,190 --> 00:32:21,360
Should I just watch my father die?

717
00:32:23,080 --> 00:32:25,640
I understand what you are trying to say.

718
00:32:26,120 --> 00:32:28,389
All of us are filial sons.

719
00:32:28,390 --> 00:32:30,310
However, understanding alone is useless.

720
00:32:30,430 --> 00:32:31,989
We can't solve the problem.

721
00:32:31,990 --> 00:32:33,949
We need to look at the situation.

722
00:32:33,950 --> 00:32:35,030
Right?

723
00:32:35,520 --> 00:32:38,310
Forcing your own brother.

724
00:32:38,710 --> 00:32:40,680
Do you think that's right?

725
00:32:44,080 --> 00:32:45,790
It just gives us chills

726
00:32:46,080 --> 00:32:48,360
that he won't even do
the kidney compatibility test.

727
00:32:48,430 --> 00:32:50,149
He just talks about money all the time.

728
00:32:50,150 --> 00:32:52,229
Even so, it's still a good thing.

729
00:32:52,230 --> 00:32:54,149
That means he is willing to contribute,

730
00:32:54,150 --> 00:32:55,119
right?

731
00:32:55,120 --> 00:32:56,189
Isn't your previous request

732
00:32:56,190 --> 00:32:58,310
for him to pay the maintenance?

733
00:32:58,560 --> 00:33:00,759
Now, you have changed your request
and want his kidney instead.

734
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:01,709
No.

735
00:33:01,710 --> 00:33:02,950
Well...

736
00:33:03,080 --> 00:33:04,799
My father insists on that.

737
00:33:04,800 --> 00:33:07,230
We don't know why he is so persistent.

738
00:33:07,390 --> 00:33:08,599
Call him on video.

739
00:33:08,600 --> 00:33:09,840
Let me talk to him.

740
00:33:16,400 --> 00:33:18,039
(Rider is delivering)

741
00:33:18,040 --> 00:33:20,040
(Arrive in two minutes)

742
00:33:28,760 --> 00:33:29,800
Madam Xue.

743
00:33:29,800 --> 00:33:31,880
(Qingcheng District People's Court)
I'm on the seventh floor.

744
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,600
I'll come and find you immediately.

745
00:33:37,950 --> 00:33:39,599
Hello, Ms. Qin
with your number ending 8643, right?

746
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:40,840
Yes.

747
00:33:41,040 --> 00:33:41,879
Sorry.

748
00:33:41,880 --> 00:33:43,510
I took a wrong turn just now.

749
00:33:44,880 --> 00:33:45,629
Here you go.

750
00:33:45,630 --> 00:33:46,759
Sorry.

751
00:33:46,760 --> 00:33:47,469
Sure.

752
00:33:47,470 --> 00:33:48,790
Thank you.

753
00:33:57,840 --> 00:33:58,799
Dad.

754
00:33:58,800 --> 00:33:59,950
Hold on.

755
00:33:59,990 --> 00:34:01,149
The judge wants to talk to you.

756
00:34:01,150 --> 00:34:01,669
Give it to me.

757
00:34:01,670 --> 00:34:03,400
Here you go. Talk to him.

758
00:34:03,950 --> 00:34:05,200
Mister.

759
00:34:05,230 --> 00:34:07,120
Can you hear us?

760
00:34:07,560 --> 00:34:10,239
Turn your face slightly to the left
and face the camera.

761
00:34:10,240 --> 00:34:10,989
Dad,

762
00:34:10,990 --> 00:34:12,719
turn your face to the camera.

763
00:34:12,720 --> 00:34:14,080
Look at us.

764
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:16,160
Let me.

765
00:34:18,390 --> 00:34:19,640
Mister.

766
00:34:19,990 --> 00:34:22,830
Yes. Look at me.

767
00:34:23,910 --> 00:34:25,279
Let me ask you.

768
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:27,830
Can you repeat your demand
for this case?

769
00:34:27,950 --> 00:34:29,199
Judge,

770
00:34:29,200 --> 00:34:31,109
I have no demand.

771
00:34:31,110 --> 00:34:33,199
I just want my son,

772
00:34:33,200 --> 00:34:34,199
my youngest son,

773
00:34:34,200 --> 00:34:35,830
to do the examination.

774
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:37,430
That's impossible.

775
00:34:37,720 --> 00:34:39,679
I will never do the compatibility test.

776
00:34:39,680 --> 00:34:43,359
I'd advise you to check whether
the equipment in our hometown's hospital

777
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:45,389
is accurate or not
since it has not been used for so long.

778
00:34:45,390 --> 00:34:46,839
I hope it's not a false alarm.

779
00:34:46,840 --> 00:34:48,109
Shut up.

780
00:34:48,110 --> 00:34:49,719
You are so heartless.

781
00:34:49,720 --> 00:34:50,909
Let me talk to my dad.

782
00:34:50,910 --> 00:34:51,960
Dad,

783
00:34:52,200 --> 00:34:53,159
don't argue with him.

784
00:34:53,160 --> 00:34:55,000
I'll donate my kidney to you.

785
00:34:55,110 --> 00:34:56,640
He'll just pay the medical bills.

786
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:59,350
Yes. I can do it, too.

787
00:34:59,470 --> 00:35:01,069
I'll also do the compatibility test.

788
00:35:01,070 --> 00:35:03,239
If my kidney is suitable, use mine.

789
00:35:03,240 --> 00:35:05,279
Just let my bother make money
and take care of you.

790
00:35:05,280 --> 00:35:07,319
Let's end this case as soon as possible.

791
00:35:07,320 --> 00:35:09,199
Your treatment
mustn't be delayed further.

792
00:35:09,200 --> 00:35:11,270
All of you are good children.

793
00:35:11,590 --> 00:35:13,080
I just want him

794
00:35:13,240 --> 00:35:16,080
to do the test.

795
00:35:18,430 --> 00:35:19,710
Mister,

796
00:35:19,887 --> 00:35:22,429
I've read your medical report in detail.

797
00:35:22,430 --> 00:35:23,719
All right.

798
00:35:23,720 --> 00:35:25,429
All of you are kind and filial.

799
00:35:25,430 --> 00:35:26,589
I just want to know

800
00:35:26,590 --> 00:35:28,710
if Sister-in-law and Brother-in-law

801
00:35:29,041 --> 00:35:31,549
know that both of you are so kind.

802
00:35:31,550 --> 00:35:32,069
I...

803
00:35:32,070 --> 00:35:34,109
Just stop pretending for now.

804
00:35:34,110 --> 00:35:36,839
If the local hospital is wrong in their diagnosis,
who will take responsibility?

805
00:35:36,840 --> 00:35:37,639
Even if they are right,

806
00:35:37,640 --> 00:35:39,600
losing a kidney still affects us.

807
00:35:40,070 --> 00:35:41,870
Old Man, please spare us.

808
00:35:41,990 --> 00:35:43,279
Their families have it tough too.

809
00:35:43,280 --> 00:35:45,830
How our families live
is none of your business.

810
00:35:47,030 --> 00:35:48,200
Old Man.

811
00:35:48,590 --> 00:35:51,589
Let me give you some advice.
Eat whatever you want at your age.

812
00:35:51,590 --> 00:35:53,589
Don't cause so much trouble.
Otherwise, their families will be ruined.

813
00:35:53,590 --> 00:35:54,469
When the time comes,
they still have to take care of you.

814
00:35:54,470 --> 00:35:55,199
Shut up!

815
00:35:55,200 --> 00:35:57,429
How dare you say something like that?

816
00:35:57,430 --> 00:35:58,560
Calm down!

817
00:36:03,760 --> 00:36:05,390
What kind of person are you?

818
00:36:06,550 --> 00:36:07,750
Judge.

819
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:09,679
I want to go to the toilet.

820
00:36:09,680 --> 00:36:10,799
Wait.

821
00:36:10,800 --> 00:36:12,839
What are you trying to do?

822
00:36:12,840 --> 00:36:14,680
What? Can't the defendant
take a toilet break?

823
00:36:16,070 --> 00:36:17,430
Take a break.

824
00:36:24,760 --> 00:36:25,640
(Under maintenance, Do not enter)

825
00:36:38,760 --> 00:36:41,230
Excuse me, is anyone inside?

826
00:36:43,470 --> 00:36:45,710
If no one's inside, I'll go in.

827
00:36:49,600 --> 00:36:51,200
(Male)

828
00:36:54,160 --> 00:36:55,520
Madam Xue.

829
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:57,710
Yes. I'm also in the bathroom.

830
00:36:59,030 --> 00:37:00,600
What a coincidence. I'll be there soon.

831
00:37:01,320 --> 00:37:02,520
Go inside.

832
00:37:05,680 --> 00:37:07,480
I'm already at the washroom.

833
00:37:07,510 --> 00:37:08,790
Madam Xue?

834
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:10,480
Is it you?

835
00:37:10,590 --> 00:37:11,790
Nice to meet you.

836
00:37:15,240 --> 00:37:16,359
I didn't go to the toilet.

837
00:37:16,360 --> 00:37:17,750
I was just...

838
00:37:17,950 --> 00:37:19,799
The trial was too intense

839
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:21,270
so I came to do my makeup.

840
00:37:21,510 --> 00:37:22,870
Did you win?

841
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:28,589
The judge did not
announce a verdict immediately.

842
00:37:28,590 --> 00:37:31,109
But it was obvious
that the judge was on our side.

843
00:37:31,110 --> 00:37:32,239
Besides,

844
00:37:32,240 --> 00:37:34,029
I usually win

845
00:37:34,030 --> 00:37:36,310
copyright infringement cases.

846
00:37:36,910 --> 00:37:40,000
Were you wearing this to the trial?

847
00:37:41,910 --> 00:37:43,429
Yes. This is my lucky outfit.

848
00:37:43,430 --> 00:37:44,319
I usually

849
00:37:44,320 --> 00:37:46,159
wear this brand on important occasions.

850
00:37:46,160 --> 00:37:48,319
I'm impressed with their design theory.

851
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:52,390
It's about confidence
and bravery in women.

852
00:37:53,510 --> 00:37:55,159
Only those who can't afford
to wear luxury brands

853
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:57,520
memorize the brand story.

854
00:38:00,200 --> 00:38:02,469
I do wear normal brands

855
00:38:02,470 --> 00:38:04,350
but I don't know their stories.

856
00:38:06,590 --> 00:38:08,640
Why don't we get down to business?

857
00:38:08,760 --> 00:38:11,389
Were you being sued
for copyright infringement

858
00:38:11,390 --> 00:38:13,480
and were demanded
compensation of three million yuan?

859
00:38:13,880 --> 00:38:14,989
Sorry,

860
00:38:14,990 --> 00:38:16,790
I don't want to deal with liars.

861
00:38:22,430 --> 00:38:23,830
Madam Xue.

862
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:27,069
Your tag is out.

863
00:38:27,070 --> 00:38:28,319
(Price 41,700 yuan,
Rental fee, 680 yuan/day)

864
00:38:28,320 --> 00:38:29,750
What tag?

865
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:32,029
Trying to fool
a client worth three million yuan

866
00:38:32,030 --> 00:38:33,799
with a rented luxury outfit?

867
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,109
You are really daring.

868
00:38:35,110 --> 00:38:36,640
That's none of your business.

869
00:38:37,680 --> 00:38:39,200
Let me give you a case.

870
00:38:40,950 --> 00:38:42,389
However, it's not
worth three million yuan.

871
00:38:42,390 --> 00:38:43,870
Are you willing to take it?

872
00:38:44,360 --> 00:38:45,600
You're crazy!

873
00:38:47,320 --> 00:38:48,680
Madam Xue!

874
00:38:55,240 --> 00:38:56,430
Su Qi.

875
00:38:58,200 --> 00:38:59,389
Why does the old man

876
00:38:59,390 --> 00:39:01,359
insist on letting the youngest son
donate his kidney?

877
00:39:01,360 --> 00:39:03,390
The elder brother and sister
have agreed to do it.

878
00:39:04,070 --> 00:39:05,549
The kid is young.

879
00:39:05,550 --> 00:39:07,120
Perhaps his kidney is better?

880
00:39:07,720 --> 00:39:09,069
They are all a family.

881
00:39:09,070 --> 00:39:10,790
They will never
think about things like that.

882
00:39:13,990 --> 00:39:15,679
If he is faking his uremia,

883
00:39:15,680 --> 00:39:17,069
that means he just wants money.

884
00:39:17,070 --> 00:39:19,000
He will be exposed after a diagnosis.

885
00:39:19,280 --> 00:39:21,520
What if he does have uremia?

886
00:39:22,070 --> 00:39:23,509
But he doesn't behave like it.

887
00:39:23,510 --> 00:39:25,069
I saw him at the hospital that day.

888
00:39:25,070 --> 00:39:27,350
He was running as fast as a deer.

889
00:39:27,590 --> 00:39:29,640
His youngest son

890
00:39:29,720 --> 00:39:30,509
was fearless

891
00:39:30,510 --> 00:39:32,310
as if he knew his father

892
00:39:32,680 --> 00:39:34,520
is just pretending to be sick
and asking for money.

893
00:39:34,590 --> 00:39:36,359
Once the case is overturned,

894
00:39:36,360 --> 00:39:38,600
he will be free of his family burden.

895
00:39:38,910 --> 00:39:40,200
Su Qi...

896
00:39:49,160 --> 00:39:51,000
I was careless.

897
00:39:53,110 --> 00:39:55,600
I got something so serious on my hands.

898
00:39:58,840 --> 00:40:01,469
(This family is acting mysteriously)

899
00:40:01,470 --> 00:40:03,040
(and trying to hide something.)

900
00:40:04,200 --> 00:40:05,799
(What are they)

901
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:08,120
(actually trying to achieve?)

902
00:40:09,880 --> 00:40:13,800
(Maintenance Case, Plaintiff: Feng Jianye,
Defendant: Feng Shengli)

903
00:40:17,840 --> 00:40:18,719
(This won't do.)

904
00:40:18,720 --> 00:40:20,520
(I must think of something.)

905
00:40:21,960 --> 00:40:24,000
(Breast Surgery Office,
Director's Office)

906
00:40:27,120 --> 00:40:28,840
(Is everything going well?
Do you have something on your mind?)

907
00:40:28,840 --> 00:40:29,200
(No.)

908
00:40:29,510 --> 00:40:30,509
Hello, Director Xie.

909
00:40:30,510 --> 00:40:31,430
Hello.

910
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:32,520
Dr. Wang.

911
00:40:32,760 --> 00:40:35,069
The hospital is arranging
a breast health awareness talk

912
00:40:35,070 --> 00:40:36,509
at the Qingcheng District People's Court.

913
00:40:36,510 --> 00:40:37,549
Are you fine with that?

914
00:40:37,550 --> 00:40:40,040
I'm going to attend
my cousin's wedding tomorrow.

915
00:40:40,280 --> 00:40:41,799
Can you find someone else?

916
00:40:41,800 --> 00:40:42,719
I just asked

917
00:40:42,720 --> 00:40:44,469
Dr. Liu and Dr. Liao at the canteen.

918
00:40:44,470 --> 00:40:45,910
All of them are also busy.

919
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:48,750
They say the family court's
health reports are very bad.

920
00:40:49,017 --> 00:40:52,107
The chief judge asked our director
to arrange it as soon as possible.

921
00:40:52,240 --> 00:40:54,910
This talk is very important.

922
00:40:54,950 --> 00:40:56,680
It cannot be postponed.

923
00:40:56,800 --> 00:40:59,600
But who am I going to find?

924
00:40:59,840 --> 00:41:01,199
Did you say

925
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:03,080
the Qingcheng District Court?

926
00:41:03,200 --> 00:41:04,520
Yes, Director Xie.

927
00:41:07,880 --> 00:41:09,120
All right. I'll go.

928
00:41:10,680 --> 00:41:12,120
That's not right.

929
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:13,910
Your time is precious.

930
00:41:14,200 --> 00:41:15,710
Let me ask Dr. Qu instead.

931
00:41:16,430 --> 00:41:17,870
It's fine. I'll go.

932
00:41:18,270 --> 00:41:20,870
Let me reschedule my meeting tomorrow.

933
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:21,509
Thank you so much.

934
00:41:21,510 --> 00:41:22,750
It's all right.

935
00:41:23,430 --> 00:41:24,830
Thank you, Dr. Xie.

936
00:41:28,550 --> 00:41:30,080
Hello, Madam Liu.

937
00:41:30,110 --> 00:41:32,639
Are you asking about
the time of the trial?

938
00:41:32,640 --> 00:41:34,199
I'm also waiting for the judge.

939
00:41:34,200 --> 00:41:34,799
When I find out,

940
00:41:34,800 --> 00:41:36,520
I'll inform you immediately.

941
00:41:37,160 --> 00:41:38,239
Ms. Qin,

942
00:41:38,240 --> 00:41:39,879
I'm sorry.

943
00:41:39,880 --> 00:41:42,000
I'm not rushing you.

944
00:41:44,590 --> 00:41:46,600
It's like this. Well...

945
00:41:46,640 --> 00:41:47,790
I...

946
00:41:47,840 --> 00:41:48,589
I...

947
00:41:48,590 --> 00:41:51,160
I want to trouble you.

948
00:41:51,720 --> 00:41:52,839
Not at all.

949
00:41:52,840 --> 00:41:54,710
What do you need? Just tell me.

950
00:41:56,280 --> 00:41:57,560
I want...

951
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:59,159
I want to trouble you

952
00:41:59,160 --> 00:42:01,040
to tell the judge

953
00:42:01,720 --> 00:42:03,790
that I'm withdrawing my lawsuit.

954
00:42:05,470 --> 00:42:06,790
Withdrawing your lawsuit?

955
00:42:08,200 --> 00:42:09,560
Why?

956
00:42:15,680 --> 00:42:16,960
Madam Liu.

957
00:42:18,280 --> 00:42:19,560
Madam Liu?

958
00:42:21,390 --> 00:42:23,239
There's no reason.

959
00:42:23,240 --> 00:42:24,799
You are my lawyer.

960
00:42:24,800 --> 00:42:27,640
Just do whatever I tell you to.

961
00:42:30,110 --> 00:42:32,279
Are you alone at home now?

962
00:42:32,280 --> 00:42:33,830
Is anyone else at home with you?

963
00:42:34,240 --> 00:42:36,029
No. I'm alone.

964
00:42:36,030 --> 00:42:37,679
Sure. Just wait there.

965
00:42:37,680 --> 00:42:39,109
I'll get a ride immediately

966
00:42:39,110 --> 00:42:40,560
and go to your house.

967
00:42:40,680 --> 00:42:42,159
Don't come to my house.

968
00:42:42,160 --> 00:42:45,239
My house is a mess now.

969
00:42:45,240 --> 00:42:46,029
Don't worry.

970
00:42:46,030 --> 00:42:48,360
I always visit my client's house.
I've seen all kinds of messy houses.

971
00:42:48,360 --> 00:42:49,560
I'm fine with any mess.

972
00:42:49,590 --> 00:42:50,239
If you don't mind,

973
00:42:50,240 --> 00:42:51,870
I can even help you clean up the mess.

974
00:42:52,800 --> 00:42:53,759
Seriously...

975
00:42:53,760 --> 00:42:54,679
Seriously...

976
00:42:54,680 --> 00:42:57,350
Why are you doing this, Ms. Qin?

977
00:42:58,360 --> 00:43:00,270
You are my lawyer.

978
00:43:00,280 --> 00:43:01,989
I am your client.

979
00:43:01,990 --> 00:43:04,160
You serve me.

980
00:43:14,620 --> 00:43:18,080
♪All the little things
between you and me♪

981
00:43:18,080 --> 00:43:20,760
♪Woven into our lives♪

982
00:43:21,610 --> 00:43:23,590
♪The building blocks of life♪

983
00:43:23,590 --> 00:43:25,290
♪Shape the sky above us♪

984
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:27,450
♪Are you doing alright?♪

985
00:43:27,770 --> 00:43:30,450
♪What are you struggling for?♪

986
00:43:31,330 --> 00:43:35,150
♪Some questions weigh like mountains♪

987
00:43:35,530 --> 00:43:40,380
♪How do we piece life back together?♪

988
00:43:40,940 --> 00:43:45,130
♪So hate can fade
and love feels new again♪

989
00:43:45,130 --> 00:43:48,200
♪Reclaim the barren parts of life♪

990
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:54,570
♪Walking this road
together, still hoping♪

991
00:43:55,360 --> 00:44:00,420
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

992
00:44:00,720 --> 00:44:04,690
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

993
00:44:04,920 --> 00:44:09,900
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

994
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:14,880
♪Where fairness stands♪

995
00:44:15,350 --> 00:44:17,590
♪Within every heart♪

996
00:44:17,590 --> 00:44:20,240
♪So many voices calling♪

997
00:44:20,500 --> 00:44:24,790
♪Struggling, lost,
waiting for an answer♪

998
00:44:24,790 --> 00:44:27,140
♪Light up the lamps♪

999
00:44:27,140 --> 00:44:29,810
♪To answer those voices♪

1000
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:32,240
♪You deserve to be happy♪

1001
00:44:32,240 --> 00:44:34,990
♪Loud and clear♪

1002
00:44:34,990 --> 00:44:37,310
♪All the little things♪

1003
00:44:37,310 --> 00:44:40,010
♪Woven into our lives♪

1004
00:44:40,830 --> 00:44:42,880
♪The building blocks of life♪

1005
00:44:42,880 --> 00:44:44,590
♪Shape the sky above us♪

1006
00:44:44,590 --> 00:44:47,040
♪Are you doing alright?♪

1007
00:44:47,040 --> 00:44:49,150
♪What are you struggling for?♪

1008
00:44:49,400 --> 00:44:51,530
♪Some questions♪

1009
00:44:52,100 --> 00:44:54,800
♪Weigh like mountains♪

1010
00:44:57,690 --> 00:45:02,840
♪Let me be the wind at dawn♪

1011
00:45:03,120 --> 00:45:07,130
♪Blowing away all the pain♪

1012
00:45:07,310 --> 00:45:12,360
♪Let me be the balance
that holds the weight♪

1013
00:45:12,730 --> 00:45:16,430
♪Where fairness stands♪

1014
00:45:16,600 --> 00:45:19,680
♪Within the law♪

1015
00:45:20,840 --> 00:45:29,520
♪And within every heart♪
